{"tid":837173,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【#Cult片】《血鸚鵡》(1981)","createTime":"2018-09-26T07:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T09:26:25.000Z","uid":212112,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58089133d79a0ebec224fcb4e98340d6e4ee76cf","tid":837173,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/152318_138f7d50e4760cd2e1cf439c2b4f336f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F152318_138f7d50e4760cd2e1cf439c2b4f336f.png&h=5c16e9dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇情講述據說幽冥中諸魔用魔血化成了血鸚鵡，只要你能看見它，就會有三個願望。江湖俠盜葉停楓與其他高手一樣，一直在追尋血鸚鵡的真相；而中原名捕「鐵手無情」鐵恨，則對王府一夜之間突告失竊的十三箱珠寶緊緊追查。一夜，葉、鐵二人在墳場相遇，血鸚鵡突告出現，鐵死於它的魔力之下&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/152320_5c7850f7f8d31b2be5c9d618b376c8da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F152320_5c7850f7f8d31b2be5c9d618b376c8da.png&h=232de984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本片由古龍原著，倪匡改編劇本，華山執導。女主角梁珍妮每次拍的邵氏電影憑片必脫；憑脫必露。她在片中造型像修羅男爵一樣，衣服只穿一邊；乳房露出一邊。<br />\n整部電影詭異而血腥，邵氏剝削片的大雜燴，最搶眼的兩場戲：梁珍妮吞下血石，雌雄同體後，居然與一顆珍珠瘋狂造愛；迷離詭譎魔穴戲，鏡子迷宮內男的用武力破陣，梁珍妮用脫衣全裸露奶露毛破陣。<br />\n整體香艷刺激，也有點噁心，蛆蟲膿漿，蚯蚓毒蛇，斷臂殘肢，再次令人深感當年電影無畏尺度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/152326_f150138767f114ce006db1e60f9947de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F152326_f150138767f114ce006db1e60f9947de.png&h=05c00911&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/152328_3afed313e1df7a95f1c84c40944e2ac7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F152328_3afed313e1df7a95f1c84c40944e2ac7.png&h=8b9d3ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/152330_4a106c0433728f41565f4ca0f4da9e90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F152330_4a106c0433728f41565f4ca0f4da9e90.png&h=efcf6677&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/152332_f3c55159a6569b5fa5a67c1a116a9345.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F152332_f3c55159a6569b5fa5a67c1a116a9345.png&h=b4650195&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/152334_d10a81b9765d77434de96682de6427c1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F152334_d10a81b9765d77434de96682de6427c1.png&h=365c5054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/BnzwkxvheUp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBnzwkxvheUp%2F&d=kfSNCAAQUomQqF8ClgZlJrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=5e17eaef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBnzwkxvheUp%2F&h=d5e31509\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/p/BnzwkxvheUp/</a>"},{"pid":"c09a8c8e016b6c7e90def8dd3da7706bd50ec3c6","tid":837173,"uid":212112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3e411e2ad54ff815601b4c98aa3792cfd606b5","tid":837173,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897dc7dbc89d4f7be7d2d2250c57ff9a531b7a36","tid":837173,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecd9ff8f5ac1f2b293de9731f25be3ec6a1251f","tid":837173,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T12:00:58.00